<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://developer.apple.com/documentation/userexperience/Conceptual/APStyleGuide/APSG_2008.pdf" class="external free" title="http://developer.apple.com/documentation/userexperience/Conceptual/APStyleGuide/APSG_2008.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://developer.apple.com/documentation/userexperience/Conceptual/APStyleGuide/APSG_2008.pdf</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.councilscienceeditors.org/publications/" class="external text" title="http://www.councilscienceeditors.org/publications/" rel="nofollow">SCE</a></li>
